{"tid":611311,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"【未有評測】淘寶國產50mm f/1.8+相機配件","createTime":"2018-03-31T00:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T06:23:43.000Z","uid":63158,"like":6,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"27fa074dc6500b9822353655918db8ed3c24822c","tid":611311,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:45:08.000Z","msg":"小弟開完po問幾時有新一代中階單反，結論係至少一年半後先會有90D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以3年一新呢個產品週期嚟講，中段時期先開始等實在係雞肋。既然我決定唔買舊機，又唔想on99呆等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以，小弟再次翻開房裏早已塵封嘅防潮箱......拎出一部&mdash;&mdash;SAMSUNG微單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機身都尚算幾乾淨靚仔，但鏡頭就發霉咁款，試影啲色好似白內障咁淺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩係APSC機嚟，有raw調吓色咁，至少唔似弱智仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n渣住支kit鏡仔好悶兼冇乜料到，所以泵幾舊水買咗支國產鏡試伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇中枝鏡有AF，遲啲upgrade可以駁住上轉Canon後繼續玩，買得唔好浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家就玩住MF先，<br />\n<br />\n機身冇Focus Peaking，要望住個三吋mon對焦，對焦應該會睇到盲(日光下應更嚴重)。所以小弟仲買埋LCD取景器，手指柄同手腕strap，希望改善到情況兼好揸手啲，同樣會包膠。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫住咁多先，等緊淘寶。有冇人有興趣睇評測？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88012751245dc9685b3bbcad2b5990a7ea595fbd","tid":611311,"uid":40445,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:53:13.000Z","msg":"微你老母單"},{"pid":"aaa1687ef8c75bb8193fe40178d33a87053435f9","tid":611311,"uid":63158,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"88012751245dc9685b3bbcad2b5990a7ea595fbd","tid":611311,"uid":40445,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:53:13.000Z","msg":"微你老母單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T01:01:55.000Z","msg":"對唔住大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9421ac7b2139de5049b73a61fb1bfbba43d126f0","tid":611311,"uid":63158,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"aaa1687ef8c75bb8193fe40178d33a87053435f9","tid":611311,"uid":63158,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"88012751245dc9685b3bbcad2b5990a7ea595fbd","tid":611311,"uid":40445,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:53:13.000Z","msg":"微你老母單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T01:01:55.000Z","msg":"對唔住大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T01:02:52.000Z","msg":"支持正體字：無反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ca563accf0066bb6e2f597e1829ef9a11e4398","tid":611311,"uid":37688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T01:05:16.000Z","msg":"無反就無反 微乜撚野單"},{"pid":"12b954cb062a604d6b237b7cc616a352ef11872c","tid":611311,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"93ca563accf0066bb6e2f597e1829ef9a11e4398","tid":611311,"uid":37688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T01:05:16.000Z","msg":"無反就無反 微乜撚野單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"對唔住大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手快打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856db7c0f520f17122568222fa0f3511c78da09a","tid":611311,"uid":54871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T01:09:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f019c5a998967e841f2e58b2f49ac7a67a9f9540","tid":611311,"uid